narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Obviously you have to write a thesis if you're majoring in Art History; obviously you won't write a thesis for Art History if it's not your major

It was a great and easy way to finish my requirement, because I could use my time when I wanted to and not go to class at the same time. I would recommend it as a great way to finish the senior thesis.
challenging and you need to be self-driven.
